CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 19, 1958, pg. B6, reads: "M. Lifsher's Work - M. Lifsher and Son, 809 E. Carson St., home improvement experts for over 28 years, recently remodeled Mrs. Syvella Williams' home on Iowa St. Mrs. Williams designed these changes and they were very ably carried out by M. Lifsher and Son.  in top photo is a view of the new kitchen, completely modernized with built-in range and refrigerator... - Harris Photo. - Adv."
TitMainTitle: View through door of kitchen remodeled by M. Lifsher and Son in home of Syvella Williams, Iowa Street
